丽庄重，气象万千，是闻名遐迩的花园式学校，教育部表彰的文明校园。 据央视新闻，2022 年，超 202 万人报考国家公务员，183 万余人通过资格审查，创国家公务员考试人数新高；平均竞争比超过 60 比 1，最热职位竞争比超过 20000 比 1。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4e4caa3c488627440c658d7442f97c48_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/590535479"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Isuubs8ebzIIDEAMaCDkzNTExNDYzIKDn2aAGMAU4sgFAMXIJNTkwNTM1NDc5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0}